Upload the contents of "install" to Pastebin.
In an Advanced Computer, type "pastebin get [pastebin token] install"
In the Advanced Computer, type "install" and press enter
Hook up 4 max size Monitors (for rules) and 4 max length/1 block height Monitors (for headers) on top.
Connect with Networking Cables and Wired Modems. Click the Wired Modems to connect the Monitors. Record the Monitor numbers.
In the Advanced Computer, type "edit startup" and change the Monitor numbers into the correct ones.


N.B.: in "API.WriteFile("General", "monitor_78", 1.5,2)", 1,5 is the font size, 2 is the spacing from the front.
